Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - It's not always easy to tell if someone is lying to you, especially at face value. In serious situations, a machine lie detector test is usually used to determine if someone is being truthful. Life coach, author, and certified human lie detector, Lizette Volkwyn, knows how to spot a lie. Lizette joined the South African Morning Team in the studio to talk about how to do just that. Watch the video above.